Greenwood Resources Inc said it has soldits 4,300,000 common share majority holding in &lt;New London OilLtd> of London to an affiliate of &lt;Guinness Peat Group PLC> ofLondon and an affiliate of &lt;Sidro SA> of Belgium for a total of1,700,0000 dlrs in cash.    The company said it will apply the proceeds of the sale tosupport its line of credit and as part of a proposed debtrestructuring with Colorado National Bancshares &lt;COLC> andGreenwood shareholders.    It said it will retain a seat on the New London board. Reuter&#3;